TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {86553=We proudly introduce our new premium fishing line, quite possibly the best fishing line in the world today! Fluorohybrid FH is a co-extruded hybrid of an advanced coplymer inner core with an outer layer of premium fluorocarbon. This line features virtually no memory, significantly smaller diameter than competitors’ same strength lines, extreme limpness, abrasion resistance and easier long casts. This line won the best line of the show at the 2008 European EFTTX fishing show and is already being highly acclaimed by many U.S. tournament professional anglers.}
